oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Rod Brasfield and Ann Young at the Mi - Da - Ga Theaters
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Brasfield, Rod, 1910-1958;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and blue on white) announcing Rod Brasfield and Miss Ann Young with Ebb Hart and the Cavaliers at the Mi - Da - Ga theater on June 6. Poster features metal photoplates of Rod Brasfield and Ann Young.
